      "date": "2020-08-24 23:17:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> This is going to break many other patches :-(\n\nTrue, but merging is trivial.\nIf only our gatekeeper were allowed to do these merges (like Linus does) rather than forcing it back on the submitter and requiring a full retest.",
